    "name": "Heavy Exoskeleton",
    "system": {
        "actionType": {
            "value": "passive"
        },
        "actions": {
            "value": null
        },
        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your chitinous plates have thickened in response to heavy punishment. Every bit of scar tissue that forms on your plates and every healed fracture have built your natural defenses into a protective layer that's truly a sight to behold. Your exoskeleton becomes heavy armor, and your proficiency in your exoskeleton armor becomes equal to your proficiency in medium armor. Your armor now grants a +5 item bonus to AC, has a +1 Dex cap, a check penalty of –2, a –10-foot penalty to Speed, and a Strength threshold of +3. It has a Bulk of 3 and the bulwark, comfort, and exposed traits. It's in the plate armor group. You can wear flight suits, but no other armor.</p>"
        },
